		<legis-type>A BILL</legis-type>
		<official-title>To impose a moratorium on conferences held by the
		  Internal Revenue Service.</official-title>
	</form>
	<legis-body id="HE9B481220D4A4577AD8FB0AE68960EC8" style="OLC">
		<section id="HA8F0B6C955844E109714A93F10D39AC5" section-type="section-one">
      <enum>1.</enum>
      <header>Short title</header>
      <text display-inline="no-display-inline">This Act may be cited as the
			 <quote>
          <short-title>Stop Playing on Citizen’s Cash
			 Act</short-title>
        </quote>.</text>
		</section>
    <section id="H33E7092A037D49C2ACDEAA0EF058E62F">
      <enum>2.</enum>
      <header>Moratorium on IRS
			 conferences</header>
      <text display-inline="no-display-inline">The <cato:entity-ref xmlns:cato="http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml" entity-type="federal-body" entity-id="2050">Internal
			 Revenue Service</cato:entity-ref> shall not hold any conference until—</text>
			<paragraph id="HAE32A59876D94CA6BD65BDB0817B10FA">
        <enum>(1)</enum>
        <text>the <cato:entity-ref xmlns:cato="http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml" entity-type="federal-body" entity-id="2014">Treasury
			 Inspector General for Tax Administration</cato:entity-ref> submits a report to <cato:entity-ref xmlns:cato="http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml" entity-type="federal-body" entity-id="0001">Congress</cato:entity-ref>—</text>
				<subparagraph id="H019E23A5971A4890835911140B74F8AD">
          <enum>(A)</enum>
          <text>certifying that
			 the <cato:entity-ref xmlns:cato="http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml" entity-type="federal-body" entity-id="2050">Internal Revenue Service</cato:entity-ref> has implemented all of the recommendations set out
			 in such <cato:entity-ref xmlns:cato="http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml" entity-type="federal-body" entity-id="2014">Inspector General’s</cato:entity-ref> report titled <term>Review of the August 2010 Small
			 Business/Self-Employed Division’s Conference in Anaheim, California</term>,
			 and</text>
				</subparagraph>
        <subparagraph id="H274294A32AF74973A60F575D19FCB3E9">
          <enum>(B)</enum>
          <text>describing such
			 implementation, and</text>
				</subparagraph>
      </paragraph>
      <paragraph id="H7160B6F924924135B9BE6AEF69409EA2">
        <enum>(2)</enum>
        <text>the <cato:entity-ref xmlns:cato="http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml" entity-type="federal-body" entity-id="2050">Internal
			 Revenue Service</cato:entity-ref> is authorized by law (enacted after the date of the enactment
			 of this Act) to resume holding conferences.</text>
			</paragraph>
    </section>
